    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-condition masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presenting in an absolute pristine state, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience for the most demanding enthusiast. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a testament to preservation and a rare opportunity to own a specimen of investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
