    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiasts! I\u2019m putting my absolute pride and joy up for sale, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed with love. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking and driving just like it did the day it left the showroom. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for by someone who truly loves cars, you\u2019ve found it! Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a surgically maintained E92 M3 that redefines the standard for the S65 platform. This high-revving V8 has been treated with clinical precision; rod bearings were proactively replaced with treated shells and ARP bolts to ensure bottom-end longevity, while the throttle actuators feature upgraded gears for zero-fail reliability. The powertrain exhibits perfect volumetric efficiency with a linear power band that pulls hard to the 8,400 RPM redline. Chassis-wise, the EDC dampening remains sharp, and the subframe shows zero deflection or stress fracturing. The DCT software has been optimized for lightning-fast shifts and rev-matched downshifts that are perfectly synchronized with the exhaust note. The exterior retains its factory depth with no swirl marks, and the interior bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless paint. Showroom interior. Mechanically perfect. First one with cash takes it. No games.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule wrapped in hand-stitched leather and polished walnut. Imagine gliding through the misty morning air, the engine purring with a velvet smoothness that modern cars have long forgotten. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of elegance and unhurried grace. It has been cherished like a family heirloom, preserved in a state that captures the very essence of its debut. To drive it is to reclaim a lost era of motoring, where the journey mattered far more than the destination. This is a rare opportunity to own a masterpiece that feels as fresh as the day it first sparked to life.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and preserved in pristine condition, this vehicle represents an uncompromising standard of luxury and performance. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of dedicated care. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands perfection. Secure a level of quality that is truly unparalleled in today's market.",
      "price": 48900.0,
